title: iCliniq
description: iCliniq is a trusted health decision platform that helps people address health concerns through personalized medical insights, AI-powered assistants, symptom checkers, and an active online community. For over 12 years, iCliniq has been top-rated by Parade and Insider, trusted by 100M+ patients and 4,500+ physicians across 80+ specialties in 190+ countries.We provide accessible, reliable healthcare while delivering valuable data and fostering informed decision-making for both patients and doctors
